p: Subpoena Territory of Washington County of Lincoln}ss To John Cody: In the name of the United States, You are hereby required to appear before the undersigned, one of the Justice of the Peace in and for said County, on the 27th day of February 1885 at 4 o'clock PM, at his office Sprague W.T. to give evidence in a certain cause then and there to be tried between the Territory of Washington Plaintiff and E. Romick defendant, on the part of the Territory Given under my hand this 27th day of February 1885 E.F. Pendleton Justice of the Peace
